# nwc-viewer: keep lib/, inflate.min.js, and the parts of the full
# viewer app needed to render/play scores in the browser. Excluded:
# the large test corpus (nwcs/), the .sf2 soundfont (falls back to a
# wavetable synth), and WebMscore (lazy-loaded, only for MuseScore
# import — fails gracefully without it), plus dev-only cruft.
